      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of heart? This car is a fantastic opportunity for someone who values character and reliability! It\u2019s in fair condition, showing some honest wear from its time on the road, but it remains a solid performer that\u2019s ready for many more miles. If you're looking for a practical vehicle that gets the job done with a smile, this is the one for you!",
