      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a reliable source for parts? This car is in poor condition and will need some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, but it offers a great opportunity for someone handy! It's an honest fixer-upper with plenty of potential for the right owner to bring it back to life.",
