    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no scratches, dings, or chips to be found. Inside, the cabin looks and smells brand new, with the leather upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at the dealership. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a new model, complete with all original documentation and two sets of keys.",
      "price": 48500.0,
