    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine and transmission perform reliably, and all essential electronics are in working order. You can expect a clean interior and a solid exterior, though there are minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with normal use. It is a dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality car that is ready for the road.",
