    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, preserved in showroom condition with no discernible wear or mechanical compromise. Every surface and component reflects meticulous care, offering the discerning buyer an investment-grade acquisition that transcends the typical pre-owned market. Experience automotive excellence in its purest form.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
