    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I've babied this car since day one! Not a single scratch, dent, or worry to be found, and it still has that wonderful new-car smell. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin, you're going to fall in love! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
