    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, a definitive specimen of Bavarian engineering. This vehicle is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously calibrated for optimal cam phasing. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a GKN-sourced M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with no bushing deflection. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been maintained to an exacting standard, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is reached with surgical precision. A concours-ready example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
